<span id="freeTextContainer6363388291420532672">5☆ A Raunchy Thriller <br/><br/>A raunchy Thriller that contains Murder, sex, violence, prostitution, secrets, lies, stalking and friendship.<br/><br/>Three best friends, one deadly stalker, secrets and lies, but which one is the stalker after!<br/><br/>As he lurks in the shadows...click...click....click.... the sound of his camera documenting every detail for his ultimate pleasure later.<br/><br/>The complex characters were well thought out. Each one flawed in their own way.<br/><br/>I absolutely loved reading this Taut psychological Thriller </span>
  <span id="freeText6363388291420532672" style="display:none">5☆ A Raunchy Thriller <br /><br />A raunchy Thriller that contains Murder, sex, violence, prostitution, secrets, lies, stalking and friendship.<br /><br />Three best friends, one deadly stalker, secrets and lies, but which one is the stalker after!<br /><br />As he lurks in the shadows...click...click....click.... the sound of his camera documenting every detail for his ultimate pleasure later.<br /><br />The complex characters were well thought out. Each one flawed in their own way.<br /><br />I absolutely loved reading this Taut psychological Thriller <br />It was a tantalising, dark deliciously twisty thriller that built up suspense along the way.<br />Never quiet knowing when the stalker was about to strike.<br /><br />This book does contain sensitive issues and graphic scenes of sex, rape, murder, gay sex and prostitution and stalking which some readers may find difficult to read.<br /><br />If you enjoy Taut Chilling psychological Thrillers, that sizzle with sexual tension, then you will really enjoy The Penance List.<br /><br />Thank you to Rachel Random Resources for this copy which I reviewed honestly and voluntarily.<br /><br />My Review is also on my blog website:<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://dashfan81.blogspot.com/2018/04/blog-tour-penance-list-27418.html">https://dashfan81.blogspot.com/2018/0...</a></span>
