              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7997643-donna-maguire?shelf=psychological-thriller-horror">psychological-thriller-horror</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2376859223" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14494661770534063950"><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://donnasbookblog.wordpress.com/2018/04/30/blogtour-review-for-the-penance-list-by-s-c-cunningham-sccunningham8-rararesources/'>https://donnasbookblog.wordpress.com/...</a><br/><br/>I recently had an interview with this author on my blog and after seeing her responses and enthusiasm for her books I knew I needed to read one, so when the tour came up for Penance List I jumped at the chance to join in!<br/><br/>Well I have to say wow after reading this book!! It was so much more than I expected and I thoroughly enjoyed it - it had sex, murder, secrets and lies and it was a brilliant thriller. I was hooked straight away and enjoyed every page - ve</span>
  <span id="freeText14494661770534063950" style="display:none"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://donnasbookblog.wordpress.com/2018/04/30/blogtour-review-for-the-penance-list-by-s-c-cunningham-sccunningham8-rararesources/">https://donnasbookblog.wordpress.com/...</a><br /><br />I recently had an interview with this author on my blog and after seeing her responses and enthusiasm for her books I knew I needed to read one, so when the tour came up for Penance List I jumped at the chance to join in!<br /><br />Well I have to say wow after reading this book!! It was so much more than I expected and I thoroughly enjoyed it - it had sex, murder, secrets and lies and it was a brilliant thriller. I was hooked straight away and enjoyed every page - very well written and very well put together with a brilliant writing style!!<br /><br />Definitely a 5 star read for me - sooo good!!</span>
