  <span id="freeText13566564704097878342" style="display:none">SCCunningham writes kickass RomThrillers (book/film/TV) and as respite from crime, a fun educational Children's series (3-8ys)<br /><br />Her thrillers are a skilled mix of fueled tension, dark humor and pulsating passion. Having worked in the industries she writes about, she offers a fresh level of sincerity and authority, rare in fiction.<br /><br />Her novel THE DEAL is in film development.<br />"I'm lucky to have in your novel such an embarrassment of riches to work with."<br />Writer/Producer Daniel Blake Smith.<br /><br />Her empowering, good-values Children's books help our young surf life's tricky stuff. Encouraging conversation with their grown-up on things that may be bothering them. <br /><br />An ex-model, British born of Irish roots, she married a rock musician and worked in music, film, sports, crime (CID, Crime Investigations, Wanted/Absconder Unit, Major Crime Team, Intelligence Analyst). <br /><br />Supported Causes; Veterans. Mental Health. Animal, Environment &amp; Child Protection.<br /><br />AUDIBLE<br /><br />Narrated by Susan Knight<br /><br />AMAZON<br /><br />UK <br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/S-C-Cunningham/e/B002L3ZC2U/">https://www.amazon.co.uk/S-C-Cunningh...</a><br /><br />USA<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.com/S-C-Cunningham/e/B002L3ZC2U/">https://www.amazon.com/S-C-Cunningham...</a><br /><br />CANADA<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.ca/S-C-Cunningham/e/B002L3ZC2U/">https://www.amazon.ca/S-C-Cunningham/...</a><br /><br />INDIA<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.in/S-C-Cunningham/e/B002L3ZC2U/">https://www.amazon.in/S-C-Cunningham/...</a><br /><br />YOUTUBE<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/siobhancunningham8">https://www.youtube.com/user/siobhanc...</a><br /><b